Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because your echoing voice \Nwill stir up the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.31,0:00:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.12,0:00:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,make sure you keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.69,0:00:18.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on a date with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,April 30, 2008
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:33.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Night Duty Room – Hakuou Academy Noon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What with it being Golden Week and \Nall, the Academy sure is quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.02,0:00:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great that I got my own homeroom, \Nbut I need a pay raise to go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a drag!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even get into the \Nmood to grade the tests!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, guess I'll have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Golden Week, ya gotta go to Hawaii!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gardens of the Saginomiya Residence 1:00pm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.61,0:01:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?! I was puttin' up with \Nthe chill and buildin' up the mood here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.16,0:01:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Nagi and the others are going \Nto the Aegean Sea this year, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't ya go with 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I felt I should not \Nintrude on those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, I suppose that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna get every volume of the \Nshows the boss said he wanted to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.74,0:01:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rental Video Tachibana 1:30pm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-What do they want?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:25.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The "Godfather" series maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.54,0:01:27.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or "Battles Without Honor and Humanity"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.58,0:01:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's direct-to-video V-Cinema \Nstuff, getting it all will be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.81,0:01:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have all the for-rental \Nvideos of "Brave Exkaiser"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.21,0:01:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.52,0:01:40.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.31,0:01:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what 'bout videos of \N"Superhuman-Machine Metalder"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.35,0:01:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.22,0:01:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, we've got all \Nof "Fight!! Ramenman", too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sanzenin Residence 2:00pm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the main stage today will be Mykonos \NIsland, where the Miss is vacationing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means those of us stuck at \Nhome will have no more scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a nice long break for \Nonce might not be so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I just heard someone talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be hearing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what's a nice long break when \Nit comes in the final episode?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hearing things again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:31.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Zettai nante shinjinai!\N I don't believe in absolutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:34.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukanou nante nai! \NNo such thing as impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:40.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirai wa hiraku te no naka ni aru\N The future is in the open palm of my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:45.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Honne o misecha make datoka \NStuff like, showing your true feelings means defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:50.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dentaku hajiku jinsei datoka\N Or a life tapping away at a calculator
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:55.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro o itsuwaru kurai nara\N Rather than be false to myself like that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:03:01.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichiten-battou baka-shoujiki mo kuuzen-zetsugo! \NI'll struggle to be uniquely naïve and honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:06.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Komatta kao o mireba ki-ni-naru shi\N If I see a troubled look, I'll be concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:11.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Jinsei isogu riyuu mo betsuni nai shi \NAnd it's not like I've got a reason to hurry through life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:17.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Takara no chizu wa kimi ni azukeyou \NI'll entrust you with the treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:23.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuou-mujin yori-michi datte tsukiau yo! \NI'll even keep you company on your free-ranging detours
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rakkii-sugiru tenkai \NA development that's way too lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotae wa mayowanai \NI won't hesitate to give my answer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:34.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kantan sa! Subete wa kimi no tame ni \NIt's easy! It's all for you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuuhyou wa ki-ni-shinai \NI won't worry about the rumors
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rettou-kan ni doujinai!\N I won't let a sense of inferiority get to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:45.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakedasu shunkan wa ima koko ni aru \NThe moment to start running is right here, right now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! So this is the Aegean Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Miss, you hurry up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mykonos Island, Greece
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, this is your \Nfirst time on Mykonos, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I often used to go deep-sea \Nfishing in the cold seas,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I've been to Iturup Island and \Nthose kinds of places, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you didn't get arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, the ocean is incredibly beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Clear Black LCD of the TV \Nis beautiful, too, so I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did the Miss become like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? She has always been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, some of it really can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything we could do for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:43.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Cappadocia, Turkey
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so this is Cappadocia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is what they mean when \Nthey talk about magnificent views!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so people used to \Nlive among those rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look, look, Hina, that sort \Nof looks like a camel's hump.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it really does look like a camel's hump!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a {\i1}real{\i0} camel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! Enough with the jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come enjoy the scenery from this \Nhigh vantage point a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine! I'm fine right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know I don't like high places, Ayumu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say you don't like high places, \Nbut you were able to get on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was totally asleep before we took off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not getting up until we \Nland, no matter what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, you didn't \Nhave anything to eat on the flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it was 13 hours long...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, scenery is something you \Nenjoy from a lower altitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came all the way here on vacation, \Nbut you don't seem very excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to get excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go outside. Outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get more excited under the blue sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then are you going to stay \Ninside for the whole trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there. We can go shopping \Ntogether or something later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, but, the Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that's not something I can change...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I'll stay here \Nthe whole time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sheesh! Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, I'll go out in the morning for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But just for a bit, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry you always have \Nto go to such trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time flies. It's already \Na month into the new term.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of Nagi for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Miss is becoming \Nmore used to the new class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like for her to finally \Nproperly attend school this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The developmental technology \Nfor UFOs got sold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back! How was Cappadocia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It had long lashes, a split \Nnose, and it spit on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the {\i1}real{\i0} camel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onto Greece tomorrow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to the Parthenon. \NIt's a one-story building.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's built on top of the Acropolis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll be going to \NMykonos Island after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Hayata and the others \Nare there, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, so this is Athens!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is incredible! You can see \Nthe whole city from the Parthenon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:10.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Parthenon, Greece
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this view definitely \Ndeserves to be a World Heritage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, why are you intently \Nlooking only at the temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This temple is the World Heritage! \NThe view has nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, there you go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're missing out if you \Ndon't enjoy this view.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine! I told you, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to see views from high places!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Miki and the others \Nanyway?! Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's sightseeing, you could \Njust bring them instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of them said they got tired of \Nsights like this back in kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.36,0:08:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those damn bourgeois girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they partied hard yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they asked to be left \Nat the hotel to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until it's time to take the \Nship to Mykonos Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for that, you were \Npartying hard, too, Ayumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why are {\i1}you{\i0} so energetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:08:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this is my first trip with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a trip to deepen \Nour friendship, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:06.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For some reason, I always end \Nup in high places with Ayumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-About Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Where's the view good from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um... The view in this direction is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't let go of my hand! Don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we've come to a magical land, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's true that this view \Nhasn't changed in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if time has stopped for this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Does that mean you've been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like, we used to live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Maria and I have spent \Nmore time abroad than in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, no matter where we \Nwent, you were always shut-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you really should stop being so withdrawn
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and become a child who plays \Nunder the sun as children should.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I-Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, just thinking there was a guy who \Nonce said something like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even remember what he looked like,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he was a thief and a liar, and \Na guy who couldn't keep a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave it to me, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are, Miss. As you \Ncan see, your hat is safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you shrunk, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a thing to say to \Nsomeone you've just met!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look it, but I am \Ngrowing swiftly every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pardon me. I mistook you for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear! Give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You cannot take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that hat belongs to Miss Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this hat belongs to me, \NNagi Sanzenin, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be! This bitsy kid is Miss Nagi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me bitsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:10.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which means... No... Just because \Nanything can happen in this anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:11.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Surely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:15.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've suddenly time traveled to the past?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:19.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, no matter what, that can't possibly be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:20.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, there's just no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is today's date?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peperoncino?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neapolitan, spaghettino carbonara?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ack! He's a foreigner, so \NI can't understand him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, commoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am in a hurry. Do not make any \Nmore trouble for anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Are \Nyou a kidnapper, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not! I'm no kidnapper...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, it's because of people like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:01.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At any rate... At any rate, why \Ndid I travel into the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:03.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can figure that out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I do not want to go outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to switch up my thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:17.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If this is the past and this child \Nis the Miss as a little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:19.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I start now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:23.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I start now, I can fix \Nthat super-indoor lifestyle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:25.26,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if I do, she might \Nbe able to become a girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:27.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who genuinely feels moved by \Nthe blue oceans and skies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, commoner, what are you \Nsmirking about all on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll do it! It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:35.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:38.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will use my abilities to change the Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on a date with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, a first class lady should be a \Nchild who plays under the sun as children should.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please come spend a little time with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I won't mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how to put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being targeted by Mafia \Nkidnappers right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing being targeted \Nby bona fide Sicilian Mafia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy for you to ask! It's \Na problem for me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barbeque, hotcake, soft serve ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:39.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"I've lost visual on target!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:46.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Send the next assassin."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Italian stallion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I do not like going outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:02.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:05.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's because she's had experiences \Nlike this since she was little...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:07.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why she stays indoors like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Miss! Let us go to the \Nocean together to go stargazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things always happen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not wish to go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past or the future, \NI will always protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let us go together...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me to go stargazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Then it is a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we take those guys \Nout before we go stargazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take those guys out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How in the world will you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For all the cool posturing, you're \Nawfully reliant on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pacific saury are cheap today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:05.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Not so fast!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ich liebe dich!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:31.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"We're going after them!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comment allez-vous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:32.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"They're not getting away!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect you, without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:08.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Where did they go?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Erika!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:09.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Find them!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ebi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leah Dizon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:10.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't let them get away!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have faith in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:22.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Prepare to meet your fate!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cabaret club!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to borrow this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nabeshin, Nabeshin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:33.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Uh, where did they disappear to?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddamn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:55.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"What has my life been..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is all over, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have put holes in your precious hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. It's a testament \Nto how you protected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had not saved me, \NI may have died here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... The reason I was \Nsummoned to the past was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:19:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, as promised, shall we do \Nsome stargazing here together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Call my name so that it reaches me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Because your echoing voice \Nwill stir up the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(485,127)}Liar
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Reach out that hand to hold mine
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}It'll bring a smile to my face
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Come on, let's go, we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}...look at the present and start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Maria and I have been \Nworried for you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what are {\i1}you{\i0} doing here, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... W-Well, what does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(485,127)}Liar
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just getting back at \Nthat idiot, who made me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}At a brisk pace, all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Without even noticing what color the sky was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time difference between Mykonos \NIsland and Japan is minus 7 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}I simply walked
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right about now, they are probably gazing \Nupon the beautiful starry sky of the Aegean Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}I want to be loved, to feel that touch
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, we alone must remain at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to comfort me, Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks to that, I have \Nthis quality time with you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}The sense of continually seeking
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have never gone stargazing \Njust the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Used to darken my days
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not that I want to gaze up at \NNerima's murky night sky with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see, so you're lonely, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Until the day I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, there, there! There, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These children are my life. Just kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Call my name so it echoes to the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? Yer still up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose Hayate is also gazing upon \Nthe same starry night sky on Mykonos Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:21:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Even lost, with the two of us, surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe. But the sky over there's \Nprobably filled with more stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}When we start walking, the \Nworld will come to our side
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the constellation Boötes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next to it is the Big Dipper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And beyond that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? There is a leak in the roof there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I'll take you to see the \Nstarry night sky of the Aegean Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Morning will come
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}And we'll feel the wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I will be looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you thinking about, Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wondering if Nagi and the others \Nare looking at the same stars, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}For you, I will remain by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:40.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, Nagi. She said she was going to look \Nfor Hayate and that was the last...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}All through the flowering season
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}And for all time beyond that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, the stars certainly are \Nbeautiful, aren't they, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going stargazing outside once \Nin a while isn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}It's my wish to stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you... for protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.35,0:22:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.04,0:22:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you in the future, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namae yonde boku ni todoku-youmi\NCall my name so that it reaches me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.39,0:22:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibiku koe wa kaze o okosu kara\NBecause your echoing voice will stir up the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.30,0:22:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daijoubu\NIt'll be okay
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.73,0:22:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namae yonde sora ni hibiku-youni\NCall my name so it echoes to the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.81,0:22:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayoi-michi mo kitto futari nara\NEven lost, with the two of us, surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.78,0:23:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arukidasu toki sekai ga mikata ni kawaru\NWhen we start walking, the world will come to our side
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.87,0:23:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asa ga kuru\NMorning will come
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.36,0:23:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bokura wa kaze o kanjite...\NAnd we'll feel the wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsunaida te to te hanasanai\NI won't let go of your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoritainda\NI want to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.01,0:23:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saa ikou bokura wa\NCome on, let's go, we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.35,0:23:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ima o mitsumete aruki-hajimeru\N...look at the present and start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.35,0:23:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.55,0:23:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
